$segment3/90 // Buck: Here's another question of a sort of different theme.
$segment3/91 // Buck: I feel like, we know a lot of people who focus on AI takeover risk, but I feel like AI takeover risk is, like, not that much of my uncertainty over how good the future is.
$segment3/92 // Buck: I think there are several issues that are basically as large or maybe larger, in terms of my uncertainty over how well the future will go.
$segment3/93 // Buck: Where, like, one is AI takeover risk, another is, very unfortunate human concentration of power risks, another is there is no unfortunate human concentration of power, but humans made terrible choices about what to do with the future and almost all the value is lost.
