$segment3/694 // Buck: And, basically, I felt like there was this when I came to App Academy, the people who were there were mostly people who were, like, substantially older than me and, many of whom had kind of, like, had one career out of college and then kind of failed at it or kind of, like, felt like their lives were not going the way they wanted.
$segment3/695 // Buck: And so they had this desperate energy to do something else.
