$segment3/1078 // Ryan: I looked at a bunch of, like, sort of, like, second order and third order, like, plots of layouts of things and, like, tried to understand what was causing the model to do that and was trying to, like, one, breakdown.
$segment3/1079 // Ryan: I was trying to sort of break down the language model into, like, a bunch of different orders of terms.
$segment3/1080 // Ryan: And then also, like, try to get some understanding of what each of those terms was doing and, like, decompose it and figure out terms that I could, like, simplify away or reduce to zero.
