$segment3/1691 // Buck: I think, like, the most interesting findings are various ways that, AIs having to attack over multiple actions being more painful for them than you might have guessed and, like, riskier for them than you might have guessed because of all these things we can do while we resample them, puddle the way through a trajectory, and use that to incriminate them and so on.
