$segment6/218 // Buck: For example, I think that AI control will go a lot better if you're able to use computer security like techniques where you make it so that your AIs less often have affordances that are scary so that you have more resources to look into actions that they take when they do have the affordances that are scary.
$segment6/219 // Buck: And there's a bunch of stuff like this.
