$segment6/804 // Buck: People currently are not handling this with a computer skill security skill set.
$segment6/805 // Buck: Like, the computer security people are not focused very much on this.
$segment6/806 // Buck: I think they could probably make a reasonable amount of a difference on this.
$segment6/807 // Buck: So that's just one thing that comes to mind.
$segment6/808 // Buck: I'm excited for more writing on AI safety.
$segment6/809 // Buck: I'm excited for more of a wide variety of types of media.
$segment6/810 // Buck: I'm excited for activism related to AI safety, and mid career professionals would be valuable for that kind of thing as well.
$segment6/811 // Buck: I think also, I wish there were more like economists and political scientists who and I guess, like, for a lot of these classes of expert, it feels to me like I really want them to not just try to use their skill set that they've been practicing for the last twenty years or whatever.
$segment6/812 // Buck: I want them to sincerely try to study and learn the AI stuff.
$segment6/813 // Buck: Like, I think a lot of the time mid career professionals are like, well, you know, I'm a lawyer.
